@BoringSaaSGuy I've used paid ads very successfully in SaaS.  

The key comes down to your price point.  If your price point is not high enough, you won't make it pay.

Never made it work w/out: 

(a) a sales team calling the leads, &amp; 
(b) sales team really good at selling annuals.

